{
  "stem": "17001.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when I say that they were in a hurry to shipping them out, well, my father used to tell us stories about his experience in-- during the war.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he would tell us that he was captured and he was stealing raw potatoes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we children opened our mouth and we said that how could you eat raw potatoes?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He said, my dear children, when you hungry, you are happy to have raw potatoes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of course, we said, you didn't have a chance to cook it or bake it?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He said no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then he also said that whenever they were traveling, taken by the-- the-- the-- cattle train, the best thing is if you go in and you try to find the place that your back is against the side of the train, because if you are in the middle, people will step on you.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this way, you have support for you back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when I had seen that, that these people were taken away, then it came to my mind when the Jewish people were taken away from Egypt that they were carrying the dough on their back, and that's why we celebrate Passover with the matzohs.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, my goodness.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "History repeats itself.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I told my mother, I said, they taken away many of the valuables.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Good food was left over, which means it must have been in a hurry.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I said, they going to take us soon also.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we were getting ready.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We-- we were preparing ourself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, because by that time, you got so hardened that it was a natural thing, that because you are a Jew-- because you are a Jew.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No crime was committed, but you were a Jew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one day, the gendarme comes over.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
